Apktv3z9wBjjXN6HFoGS/7" target="_blank"&gt;其他经济刺激&lt;/a&gt;。金融监管机构还将谈论如何支持经济和稳定市场。高盛降低了&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/PjIfOgIpQz9obxo9JAEqT-EYoEMqD2U2hD_cojg5-qWRSQ3JuqstCynveViXEWUraDpK3cbLe-Bqrpa8-PE1IOoHm_Nd5rOrV_2eR7l3r4fTbaSyq9r01oEt7qABuZRkATnDVhIETUC4qDWDWcW2qtQboMxbNjZmA1Rcq9f-IT9DxbCFToNYfgNDh0Y5HePh6_tc3T5pO2nlYHzuLdilttDEatDXw1V3TtKRBK4GuCIrQZ-NRj_cU2lgxseLCPqnVX10GKJ6-0M4jCPWicep2O5V_ch82iegWZI7BFea0lRfoeqvipDyDC8rsolr67tgVmArn_XgOqhmsRwmwOMyw7-3x4JeoGJ-bnmewNAAMDc43s6q4n9CEBc3qUw/uNHvSI3GjAeNOgm7e_T_gSILlpmrJDrq/7" target="_blank"&gt;中国的增长预测&lt;/a&gt;，这表明北京很难完全抵消关税的负面影响。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;美联储官员&lt;/strong&gt;准备&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/kLj3iF3nPXvkV7KCqHEFoL09K73ixdZw1WYrxshbyfx7DNYPNBW1y00VLKa4CXuLPQa5CPJr5rm8uP6PLY045N4umgwQndNnZIzypOCwYpceS5WdgYQUbxbxv3wLLBbw8vBXoypQaqNjMUmZdCZk5h6c9z9iu1foKgtPiQ7Hsl7Gc1ulis3kneg7SEHeYahIJTi4e9Y5Pjl1TtJKfU8niEjpTDJYc0tgr30tOblz1LQUSVldY0Yq_1KPVii0xZvbYcpPsCaC_oVN8T2bdn4AEtsxo8JdphDZwp5jHeCchmT9EQFciEhMX1r_I-HWef3Bjy4y_AdWLApGZ8cJrIRwGLd3unqaEjdxRkgCOf-G7rUw_h1Z3jI9471BCG0/xg33MNBFducweFolRdEEwZp5BpIuZ4G0/7" target="_blank"&gt;保持其政策利率稳定，&lt;/a&gt;以最大程度地降低特朗普的关税会导致通货膨胀持续上升的风险，即使劳动力市场进一步缩小。上个月的会议距离表明他们已经开始&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/P0kLT8FElUm68kIAT5BGQo58z0vt-6P_3BGbhcbS6wbY8uQ4whQvoox0sIItgh6MTlWLkTK9MohQjE42RvLGxXd0pjaGpUO9TOfPZTBDA7L6tLRkdw4H0-ckSDErpKTJKfu8TPZR1ldtn9Xfx4bfbM1UAVKzHJmnVsNZ6fabJ20RLrL5gM552qrjL6cccbd20w5YpB94UTy4LwmmYYKIOrOEiMRPrtzQpiXI--QtD7XJNb-dlk0VWm8glFyBP3UYABeCKGsrsMg_m9gou_vhETsNmYrMoyjSrgnuSLktmZfCuCEg0w5ysgNuE_8Ul6HpNGEOlCJiAXQSPPMRij1HCanphL-4_vK2J3FLDCq49DWPIlNU8-ybROS6O4o/nQlwYKth3XirbmjK_fxWx8eDKbs1ejcQ/7" target="_blank"&gt;担心滞水&lt;/a&gt;。一位官员Neel Kashkari说，现在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/PeUzNbGZAgzzFUoPprQUBu8dV6L0PULQMFTfi7PSUm-PLWiDID5Wt4JG5oj0sTSuakrVWhX37UTfqX_UleD9iw851jakAdystO1UIAIYixGW7xuMcVyH3pLnzRPtTQev2juOlxYhYVS7fVNP2Xga1ctjnrgfTX7ZeO1swLmB2I674Wy5vVQW066KX-Kd18v4CF0vmg4t2i19la6BqXm2F9CGsbdqZx2I9DLqiVQQQ3JPNA8TATG1IFzfkdkGtcD3qCZdRSO2Z_8UVuaqlxKcxsdmHdR84cSFeGNsLRxdOzkHExXEG9cQbxRnTl0s0i0xyceusVXJrsy8Q2rUL7ydCC-1CPnvmursn4TKcmOr0_8pOroASTWrKyYFSJk/lK7rvkzjUyaZRQi9nMcyFSPdON9Swvr6/7" target="_blank"&gt;降低利率的标准&lt;/a&gt;现在更高。&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;说到通货膨胀&lt;/strong&gt;，我们今天获得每月的CPI数据。美国的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/xBXTgZCkvBYUFlvwn5d84MPU3V0BDeLp14PtRxoI-0o2vWhwSyKCGPPCVDZ3EtD9Ay0fjbknHAYmo6GvGhJbJeHLOvuu-HPdWPYLc7RkLJU1ZXYq8WgWD4U8R5mwU1bj1yWiyd7NeyOFzO-RBFimPZRVVaC29klnbRtMNwZwF8ZGOtigpWXDwIbefHjPnJ7SKliZP6ZbaIvdvLBXttSFJtOYhKoSk9eLzzlOGLXzays78v-TVNQo174Lh0_FxNEzCjqLCpOez_EuSck2ZBj5SXa2_AYk7pZ6piwaQNeQ9G1_VTzKX48Q9aZ8Qxv0yMHb79hLrdXobBL4hpiQATrSP7XpDW2heGRUdDE6VQZyT1Et5SocBTEaCaz24CE/oOaAmgU390rLhU6towejCUsBnugkVrSS/7" target="_blank"&gt;通货膨胀可能在三月份辞职&lt;/a&gt;，部分原因是能源成本下降，在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/u1BQNm9BRRrD0J9cCZa0k6MaG940Vw7tKxKKJzMNJJA2CFYy5T2eoTZv1WYQzLUIFG6t1mTW9whCalVyRrvYit1lvsrFIAwNI1Nw5WIumm3WuAocTipdAfnAJ8wa09E0lSXGtmb_R7DC6YbXadZOzxqVpTQkzhRgXYkgmxGjllxEWvv47q2Qhp7C8S4C5RKH4NeuIyUlEr-O6IboGZEGAqyF1IUVYMxtXw5p8zO4zkzrMRhpt4xvoesGff5OJU4YKEy4n2edafK9bWVtv2l3qJRAZUYDSaW-D1x8Cp40sW4X-Xk0iyvEvATQZiaOoe8ZHrVEeWU0uxQvSDiL_wMPQVPeJnAEHJfMXNMaEOWX1z2lBxTPdwGkLBw_vho/u3W3DNoj-XtQGwjgwdw0GdPv1Nr87rWK/7" target="_blank"&gt;关税过滤&lt;/a&gt;之前为消费者提供了一些缓解。根据彭博对经济学家的调查，该指数比2月起增长0.1％。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Xbi7-gCuEX6mB6nSzM06dxdoBZ--qmAKSB8VU45ZVfWfAzeNhiqkq1QdjrXW2symNJlsrMHyRntKYsx1rBtxgbubW2sJ7e8hB8wRGTognlz5ElMiO4SR0JRSiZMTsG2uEZQ9zP7nGp3iAwD72LgqDKRdFe5Dxb_ufokYJlQ8I7gQDQHaO0r5sTLgYxd-l17S4vd6X2I_M_oadpfCqBrGWUy8Lz6ExTu0TSpnojbgEqzoMRJujVMMS5BAkwb8RLMJCH2F4R02rk5Q-FEPVPmk8Bj5ea3bk1WOGI3ZuJmM4TQwmShViPk-UUur7WnuXvGDmywA-73g34GOUookYDiSKJED3QcPl-fXGlf651mFCHt4eInH